Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:08.56,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的○○龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.61,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那個○○是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.60,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}請把後面帶有ド的詞放在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:16.94,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}「女僕」加上「龍」就是女僕龍的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:19.82,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}爲什麽非要做這種事不可啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:20.87,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}都是爲了這個企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:21.80,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}爲了企劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:24.18,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}必須要做一個番外篇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:28.05,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}這是要和TV版有區別而做的的特典映像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:29.92,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}說得真是直截了當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:32.10,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那麽我們就趕緊開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:34.02,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:36.28,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的樂隊龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:42.19,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}亂七八糟的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:44.31,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}話說對我的待遇有點過分吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.31,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}重要的是內涵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.78,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}往音樂的方向考慮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:50.93,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那衣服不是怎樣都無所謂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:52.12,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}約德爾唱法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:52.87,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}有需要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:53.98,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:55.05,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}都已經不是樂隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:56.19,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}演歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:57.59,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}音樂方向不一致
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:00:58.57,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}好了 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:00.01,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}我們都還沒出道哎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:01.61,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:04.39,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的人魚龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:05.91,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}（我們）是人魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:06.74,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:08.72,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林是我的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:10.05,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}所以說你反了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:11.56,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}我會跳舞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:12.97,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那根本不是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:13.92,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}這是特産
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:15.38,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}這應該是很糟糕的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:18.61,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}呼吸不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:19.61,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}用鰓呼吸的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:20.87,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}印度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:23.50,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的印度龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.49,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}「印度」等于「咖喱」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:27.09,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}想法很貧乏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.33,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:29.97,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}冰島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:32.91,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的冰島龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.18,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:35.68,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}新西蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:38.26,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的新西蘭龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:39.70,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}國家已經够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.20,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}鰐梨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.64,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的鰐梨龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:45.02,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}完全一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:46.19,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}裂開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.28,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}七音階
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:51.48,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的七音階龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:52.80,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}梗已經玩沒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.00,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:56.68,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的裸體龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:58.07,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}好了 逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:02.14,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}下集也是用詞後面帶ド的詞語來玩的特典映像*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:04.40,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的○○龍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:05.69,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}待續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.03,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}還會繼續的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:09.03,maidragon-text,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}
